---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About LithyLabs" description="The purpose behind LithyLabs">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
      About LithyLabs
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      <p>
        LithyLabs is a personal lab created by Jeffrey Kleiss to share projects,
        experiments, and ideas developed throughout his career.
      </p>

      <p>
        Some projects are recreations or evolutions of past work, rebuilt with
        fresh perspective. Others are active learning projects: works in progress
        meant to explore new technologies, patterns, and ways of thinking.
      </p>

      <p>
        The focus is frameworks, AI integrations, system design, and the practical
        lessons that come from building real software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
